01:37:45.543 --> 01:37:46.644
At my age?

01:37:47.427 --> 01:37:50.994
For me what counts is what people have in their
heads, and you have nothing in yours

01:37:52.042 --> 01:37:56.507
I will not be a slave of your ignorance
anymore or of your prude conscience

01:37:56.689 --> 01:37:59.363
An what about me?
I am also a slave

01:38:00.529 --> 01:38:02.858
How do you think I felt when I left the sea?

01:38:03.545 --> 01:38:06.537
All my life here, living out of this
fucking orchard

01:38:08.104 --> 01:38:10.784
To be with you.
To be only with you

01:38:11.400 --> 01:38:14.929
Me, my wife and my son.
All slaves!

01:38:32.973 --> 01:38:36.549
- Hello
- Hello

01:38:39.667 --> 01:38:42.507
