Get out of here. Get out.

01:40:46.886 --> 01:40:48.429
You are all so weird

01:40:55.628 --> 01:40:58.459
Ramon? How are you?
Wait a moment, I can't hear you

01:41:01.306 --> 01:41:05.378
- Tell me dear
- I'm leaving tomorrow

01:41:05.635 --> 01:41:08.116
Yes, Rosa told me this afternoon.
I'm sure you are impatient

01:41:08.546 --> 01:41:09.251
A little

01:41:10.371 --> 01:41:14.242
Hey Ramon, I�ve been researching
