say good bye and we shouldn't talk again

01:41:45.303 --> 01:41:49.007
Is for your security.
You shouldn't even talk to Mark about this.

01:41:51.591 --> 01:42:01.069
- Yes, yes. I understand. So this is farewell.
- Is better this way

01:42:03.253 --> 01:42:08.093
Ok, ok...ok.
Let me tell you something...

01:42:08.845 --> 01:42:12.123
Ramon, think it through all the times that is necessary.

