01:46:33.346 --> 01:46:35.218
Of course.
Since I don't move at all.

01:46:49.836 --> 01:46:53.391
Ramon. If there's really life after death...

01:46:55.799 --> 01:46:58.750
I know this is going to sound foolish, but...

01:47:01.087 --> 01:47:03.943
- Please send me a sign?
- A sign?

01:47:04.176 --> 01:47:11.759
Anything. I never was scared of spirits.
I will be very alert. Waiting. Will you do it?

01:47:12.053 --> 01:47:13.750
Of course.

01:47:14.061 --> 01:47:28.148
But, between you and me, I think that after we die
there's nothing. Just like before we are born. Nothing

01:47:30.756 --> 01:47:32.740
How can you be so sure Ramon?

01:47:33.075 --> 01:47:34.308
No one knows that

01:47:34.532 --> 01:47:36.052
